    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252290/extras/96b8bc5c83123db10eb3f9ae7256d476.poster.avif?t=1756840343\" width=704 height=396 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252290/extras/96b8bc5c83123db10eb3f9ae7256d476.webm?t=1756840343\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252290/extras/96b8bc5c83123db10eb3f9ae7256d476.mp4?t=1756840343\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Explore the island</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As you awaken on the shores of an enigmatic tropical island, you find yourself alone amidst the remnants of a bygone civilization intertwined with the echoes of a complex past. The island appears abandoned, with signs of a recent upheaval disturbing its peace.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252290/extras/8ad11447da074707ba680d7eccbf3bab.poster.avif?t=1756840343\" width=704 height=396 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252290/extras/8ad11447da074707ba680d7eccbf3bab.webm?t=1756840343\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252290/extras/8ad11447da074707ba680d7eccbf3bab.mp4?t=1756840343\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Search for meaning</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover letters left behind to piece together a narrative that drives you to understand what happened. Not all is as it appears to be on the surface, and your progression will illuminate the mysteries.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252290/extras/1d294b8fb6008e814f3d81607f86c170.poster.avif?t=1756840343\" width=704 height=396 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252290/extras/1d294b8fb6008e814f3d81607f86c170.webm?t=1756840343\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252290/extras/1d294b8fb6008e814f3d81607f86c170.mp4?t=1756840343\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Understand and observe</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Through exploration, observation, and problem solving, players must unravel the island’s secrets and discover the fate of its previous inhabitants... and themselves.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252290/extras/ab5c27cbe7b3275044b706dab377be2e.poster.avif?t=1756840343\" width=704 height=396 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252290/extras/ab5c27cbe7b3275044b706dab377be2e.webm?t=1756840343\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252290/extras/ab5c27cbe7b3275044b706dab377be2e.mp4?t=1756840343\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Unravel the mystery</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Uncover what happened to the villagers and learn why they disappeared. Explore their villages and you will find more than just hospitality. Through exploration, observation, and problem solving, players must unravel the island’s secrets and discover the fate of its previous inhabitants... and themselves.</p><p class=\"bb_